BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 328 Td (Compare a dolphin shape to an ichthyosaur picture. Notice they look similar even though not related!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 308 Td (THINK ABOUT IT:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 10 Tf 82 292 Td (Why do ichthyosaurs and dolphins look so similar despite not being related?) Tj ET

