BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 190.8 720 Td (Chapter 8: Back to Today) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 710 m 540 710 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (The twins returned to the present day, their minds full of incredible memories.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td ('It is amazing that birds are actually living dinosaurs!' Leo said.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 648 Td ('That is right! Birds evolved from small feathered dinosaurs that survived.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 632 Td (They looked out the window at sparrows hopping on the lawn.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 616 Td ('Those little guys are real-life dinosaurs!' Luna laughed.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 600 Td ('The past teaches us so much about our world,' they agreed. 'Stay curious!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 564 Td (THE SCIENCE: DINOSAURS LIVE ON!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 544 Td (Birds ARE dinosaurs! They evolved from small, feathered theropod dinosaurs.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (The link: archaeopteryx had feathers AND teeth, claws, and a bony tail!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 512 Td (All 10,000+ bird species today are technically avian dinosaurs.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 496 Td (Paleontology is the study of prehistoric life through fossils.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 480 Td (New fossils are found every year, rewriting what we know about the past!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 72 449 Td (MORAL:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F5 13 Tf 72 431 Td (The past teaches us about the future - stay curious and keep exploring!) Tj ET
